message.raw:
R now catches plotting errors
Fixed KeyError bug in aggregation
Fixed bug where ropy wasn't updated, despite insufficient version
Made R stop printing errors when searching for installed libs
Fixed error caused by trying to pass a numpy array to R via rpy2.
  This might no longer be supported by rpy2, which might cause
  many other problems.
